Simple window  decoration  with  different  menus  to  manipulate  the
window.  The  package contains all images used in the menus. It should
be   extracted   to   <tt>~/.fvwm/windowdecors</tt>.   Put    <tt>Read
$[HOME]/.fvwm/windowdecors/simple/config</tt>  at the end of your fvwm
config file and restart fvwm. The package  has  been  tested  with  an
empty config on fvwm 2.5.10. 
